{"type": "article", "id": 34635, "title": "这些设计，看起来都挺好吃｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-11-18T23:11:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 369, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161119002937eAOwDZb80MSamipd.png", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">作为生活中不可缺少的一部分，给人带来幸福感的美食们早已在脑洞大开的设计师的帮助下出现在了餐桌以外的各个地方。那些产品之所以能够成功，除了栩栩如生的还原度之外，更在于组合是否合适：比如，既保留趣味又提供舒适性，就使面包点心类成了座椅软垫类的灵感首选。本周的主题就是这些惹人嘴馋的设计。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>FINDAY by Goodeed Design</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://goodeed.design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Goodeed Design</a> 为台湾日用品牌 FINDAY 设计的浴巾包装很可能让你不知不觉就看饿了：塑料包装的上半部分印上了栩栩如生的食材，鱼和虾的肉质纹路都做得非常还原，其余部分则采用了透明的设计，还可以通过圆洞摸到里面卷起的浴巾。之所以选择寿司也是因为它简单纯粹的特质恰好与品牌所提倡的“简单又多变的生活”不谋而合，这种有趣的包装设计也启发着人们重新想象自己的日常生活。毕竟在看到这些以假乱真的大寿司之前，你可能很难想到白色浴巾和寿司竟然可以这么搭。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221413q8MIGrJ5m9UZ6RL0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221412rEaGzV73jCA2eQIo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221411ZfXt5uzNWT6Rx3o0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221410m9noXV4MpkBI1ZUC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>食パン座椅子 by Village Vanguard</h3><p class=\"\">如果你对松松软软的东西没有抵抗力，日本书屋 Village Vanguard 以面包为设计灵感的靠椅可谓种草能力十足：除了普通的白面包和烤面包造型之外，还有打上鸡蛋的吐司款和发霉的面包款。包括平放在地上当作坐垫，靠椅共有五个倾斜角度能够满足不同的需要，外套也可以拆卸下来进行清洗。脑洞大开的书屋还额外设计了煎蛋造型的大毯子和护膝毯，冬天窝在家里似乎很合适。你可以通过<a href=\"http://vvstore.jp/feature/detail/8309/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这一系列，座椅的价格从 5378 到 7538 日元不等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222245DKQVbTGAjtN4sBcr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611182222457nz8qfF3awXPDMZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222246vOM2ZRd9pCKzVUfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222246oEKcRWbxeIOG3zvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222245qRDCc1lLJZBKpTYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mon Cherry by Jenny Pokryvailo</h3><p class=\"\">以色列设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jennye589\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jenny Pokryvailo</a> 曾经为以设计有趣小物闻名的工作室&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计过一款尼斯湖怪造型的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/5660.html\">勺子</a>，这把量勺是她的最新作品。Mon Cherry 由四颗独立的“樱桃”和一片“绿叶”构成，“樱桃”可以用作量勺，“绿叶”则是一个分蛋器。用这么一款可爱的厨具组合来制作蛋糕，心情似乎也变得更加愉快。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/kitchen/products/mon-cherry-measuring-spoons-and-egg-separator\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16 美元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221712HYsFzAahMV4Dl36p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221712BamngPok1Dd80Nix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708478\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221710am4cDzEPNH6YUIwy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118221711ktAgpIuDOKBQSqRb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.434167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lollipop by Boris Klimek</h3><p class=\"\">还记得透过有色玻璃瓶窥见的世界是什么样的吗？斯洛伐克设计师 <a href=\"http://www.borisklimek.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boris Klimek</a> 为 <a href=\"http://lasvit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lasvit</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://lasvit.com/milan-2016/lights/lollipop--317/video\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lollipop</a> 灯具系列或许会让你回忆起那种多彩而有趣的体验。这些吊灯和台灯由形状不规则的有色玻璃板、金属支架以及嵌在内部的光源构成，看上去就像是把棒棒糖放在太阳下一样。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222419GNCtTfjFhDR3iKWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611182224197qLbIP5DOzQ10fEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.088750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222419OomzgTsZQhuAyCSt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222419EMaVdA2CetyprOIH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.345000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>N by NONCENSE</h3><p class=\"\">谁说线香座不可以变得有趣好玩儿？由澳大利亚一对设计师好友创立的品牌 NONCENSE 最近就以食物作为灵感设计了三款线香座，这些栩栩如生的香蕉、披萨和煎蛋均由手工打造而成。每款线香座都随印有品牌 logo 的木盒寄送，还附赠一个黑色的托特包。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.noncense.com.au/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 150 澳元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222614TRBYkNezEgyAQnfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222615eSBzjxoMQ8gTO1cL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611182226140b2HCBicwfu7pO61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118222614Fdl6IcP7Zbu9xyS0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667149\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fusion by Matthew Robinson</h3><p class=\"\">英国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.matthewrobinsonfurniture.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matthew Robinson</a>&nbsp;将核桃木和枫木结合在一起，手工打造了这把看起来像是巧克力在往下流淌的实木桌 <a href=\"http://www.matthewrobinsonfurniture.co.uk/fusion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fusion</a>。从桌面和“融化中”的桌腿可以看出，Robinson 并没有试图将两种木材简单地拼在一起，而是巧妙地让它们在结构上彼此互补，营造出一种像是来自童话故事中糖果屋的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118223044Y3ApT0U7rCMKiGSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118223046eb3D7rRhW0KvuZSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611182230443dmfCMXIHrDkWFGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161118223044Axi6f2KmW5atgvp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}